<Layout title="Diet & Nutrition - Formula 188cm">
	<h1>Diet and Nutrition Guidelines</h1>
	
	<h2>Optimal Diet Components</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>High-quality animal proteins</li>
		<li>Fresh fruits</li>
		<li>Natural dairy products</li>
		<li>Honey</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Foods to Limit</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Complex carbohydrates</li>
		<li>Processed foods</li>
		<li>Sugar</li>
		<li>Artificial sweeteners</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Special Supplements</h2>
	<p>Ginger Drink Recipe:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Extract 3-4 grams of ginger juice</li>
		<li>Mix with 300ml water</li>
		<li>Drink before sleeping</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Protein Requirements</h2>
	<p>Daily protein intake should match your body weight in grams. For example, if you weigh 70kg, aim for 70g of protein daily.</p>
</Layout>